# StudyBuddy API Docs

This repo contains the OpenAPI documentation for the StudyBuddy project.

## Structure

- `openapi.yaml`: Master file for Swagger UI
- `paths/`: Modular endpoint files
- `components/`: Shared schemas
- `scripts/`: Helper script to merge files

## How to Contribute

Each contributor edits their own file inside `paths/`.  
Use `merge_paths.py` to build the final merged file before pushing.

## Preview

Paste `openapi.yaml` into https://editor.swagger.io to view.
